<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me | Sait Elmas</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <main style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 0 1rem;">
        
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Mathematician. Engineer. Educator.</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #475569; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">
                Bridging the gap between pure mathematics, computer science, and real-world engineering to guide the next generation of analytical minds.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Grid Layout -->
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 3rem;">
            
            <!-- Left Column: Academic & Professional Journey -->
            <div>
                <h2 style="color: #3b82f6; border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">My Academic & Professional Journey</h2>
                
                <p style="color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    My path to education is built on a foundation of rigorous engineering and pure science. After earning my degree in Shipbuilding Engineering from <strong>Istanbul Technical University (ITU)</strong>, I worked as a designer and engineer on <strong>dozens of yacht projects</strong> until 2016. Driven by a deep passion for fundamental sciences, I then pivoted my career toward academia.
                </p>
                
                <p style="color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    This drive led me to <strong>Middle East Technical University (METU)</strong>, where I completed a double major in <strong>Mathematics</strong> and <strong>Computer Engineering</strong>. I am currently continuing my academic journey there as a <strong>Ph.D.</strong> student in Mathematics. 
                </p>

                <p style="color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Since transitioning to education, I have had the privilege of guiding <strong>over 100 students</strong> in achieving top ranks and maximizing their academic potential. I bring this multifaceted engineering and theoretical perspective into every lesson I teach.
                </p>

                <p style="color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Having served as an <strong>executive in corporate firms</strong> for many years and <strong>founded my own manufacturing and yacht design companies</strong>, my mission extends beyond academic success. I strive to mentor my students, equipping them with a <strong>broader vision and strategic mindset</strong> for their future professional lives. Underlying all my teaching is a deep commitment to cultivating a mindset aligned with <strong>positive global values</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column: Beyond the Desk -->
            <div>
                <h2 style="color: #10b981; border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">Beyond the Desk</h2>
                
                <!-- Modern, kırpılmış ve boyutlandırılmış fotoğraf -->
                <div style="margin: 1.5rem 0; text-align: center;">
                    <img src="/img/sait-mentor.jpg" alt="Sait Elmas" style="width: 100%; max-width: 350px; height: 350px; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 15%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                </div>

                <p style="color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Currently based in Ankara, Türkiye, I also believe that a sharp mind requires a balanced life. When I am not tutoring or coding in Python and Java, I immerse myself in the world of social Latin dances, practicing <strong>Kizomba</strong> and <strong>Bachata</strong> regularly. 
                </p>

                <p style="color: #334155; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    I am an avid reader of philosophy, particularly Stoicism, and hold a deep fascination for ancient history. Whether I am capturing moments through photography or exploring new ideas, I approach life with the same curiosity I bring to mathematics.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

